### **Step 3: Inspect the Links (Without Clicking!)**  
ğŸ“Œ **Hover over the link** (without clicking) to see where it really leads.  
ğŸš¨ **Red Flag:** If the link doesnâ€™t match the official website, itâ€™s a phishing attempt.  

ğŸ” **Example:**  
- âŒ **Fake Link:** `https://paypal-verification.com/login`  
